data.description: Offering a 3 bedroom, 2 bath  one story home on over an acre with detached 3 car garage and a 26 X 40 extended driveway. Plenty of Room for Rv, Boat, Off Road vehicles! This home has Central Heating & Air, along with a Pro Series Evaporative Cooler ducted through the house. The house interior has been painted within the last three years. Home features Luxury Vinyl and Hardwood flooring upgrades. Kitchen upgrades include granite countertops, subway tile backsplash, wine-fridge and recessed ceiling with canister lighting. The large family room has a built-in entertainment center, home has Ceiling fans throughout the home, and a large indoor laundry room. Backyard features beautifully landscaped front and back yard with block walls and a covered patio with a serving island and separate gazebo entertaining area. Property is completely crossed fenced with chain link fencing. Recreational Vehicle access with a 30ft covered RV area with 30 amp electrical wall plug. Subject property has an FHA Loan at a low rate that can be assumed!
